      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">User Interface</a> * <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">Command Line Interface</a> * Banksia</b><br />\n<b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a> * <a href=\"/Tournament_Manager\" title=\"Tournament Manager\">Tournament Manager</a> * Banksia</b>\n</p><p><b>Banksia</b>,<br />\na <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant, lightweight <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">command line interface</a> by <a href=\"/Pham_Hong_Nguyen\" title=\"Pham Hong Nguyen\">Nguyen Pham</a>, suited to run automated <a href=\"/Engine_Testing#Matches\" title=\"Engine Testing\">engine-engine matches</a>. It is open source, C++11, released under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GPLv3+</a> license, first published in July 2019 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> .\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Chess_GUI\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess GUI</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Banksia_GUI\" title=\"Banksia GUI\">Banksia GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/CLOP\" title=\"CLOP\">CLOP</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71157&amp;hilit=banksia\">Banksia - Yet another Chess Tournament Manager</a> by <a href=\"/Pham_Hong_Nguyen\" title=\"Pham Hong Nguyen\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72350\">Banksia GUI released</a> by <a href=\"/Pham_Hong_Nguyen\" title=\"Pham Hong Nguyen\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_GUI\">Chess GUI</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Chess GUI\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://banksiagui.com/\">Banksia GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/nguyenpham/banksia\">GitHub - Banksia - a Chess tournament manager</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Banksia&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71157&amp;hilit=banksia\">Banksia - Yet another Chess Tournament Manager</a> by <a href=\"/Pham_Hong_Nguyen\" title=\"Pham Hong Nguyen\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2019</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301002956\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 37/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 74/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest 